title: TRINITY ALPHA MOD BY SMOK
description: Here comes the SMOK Trinity Alpha Battery with beautiful resin streaks on both sides and 1000mAh built-in battery. The SMOK Trinity Alpha Battery US Edition is specially designed for United State market which is perfectly compatible with SMOK Trinity Alpha Pod. With the colorful resin decoration panels and outstanding designs, the Trinity Alpha Battery is a great combination of vape and art to bring an amazing visual enjoyment. The SMOK Trinity Alpha supports 10W-25W power output with three vaping modes - S(Soft)/N(Norm)/H(Hard) to meet your different vaping need. Pressing the Mode Button, you can switch the power output easily. Moreover, Trinity Alpha battery also features a unique lock button, you can fix or detach the pod easily just by pushing the button. Plus the big power button, intelligent battery life indicator and fast charging, the SMOK Trinity Alpha is definitely your best vape partner for great and easy daily vaping.Trinity Alpha Mod Features:Size: 38 x 16mmMaterial: Zinc AllyBattery Capacity: 1000mAhOutput Power: 10-25W(SOFT/NORM/HARD)Input Voltage: 3.3V-4.2VOutput Voltage: 2.4V-6.0VStandby Current: ＜200uA(No Load)/＜250uA(Load)Charger Output: DC 5V 1ACharging Voltage: 5VCharging Current: 0.7A(MAX)Compact and delicate pod battery with beautiful resin panels 1000mAh Built-in battery with ergonomically designed power buttonThree modes to satisfy different vaping demandsIntelligent battery life indicator and fast chargingUnique lock button for pod fixationPackage Includes:1 x Trinity Alpha Battery1 x USB Cable1 x User ManualWARNING: Please have a great understanding and technical knowledge on how to use this product in order to properly use it. There is always an inherent risk when using any rechargeable batteries at anytime and under any circumstances.
